8. Create a persistent volume redis-pv with below specs:
   i) hostpath /mnt/redis/data
   ii) storage size 2Gi
   iii) access mode â€“ ReadWriteOnce


ANS:

pv-def.yml
apiVersion: v1
kind: PersistentVolume
metadata:
  name: redis-pv
spec:
  storageClassName: manual
  capacity:
    storage: 2Gi
  accessModes:
  - ReadWriteOnce
  hostPath:
    path: "/mnt/redis/data"



kubectl create -f pv-def.yml

